# Optional: a dedicated Solana RPC endpoint used by the in-page Jupiter swap
# and the sniper. The public endpoint is heavily rate-limited and often blocks
# swaps, so a dedicated RPC (Helius, QuickNode, Triton, Alchemy, …) is strongly
# recommended. Copy this file to `.env` and set your URL:
VITE_SOLANA_RPC=https://api.mainnet-beta.solana.com

# Required for managed per-user sniper wallets (Privy embedded wallets).
# Create an app at https://dashboard.privy.io and paste its App ID here.
# Without it, the sniper falls back to the burner-key flow.
VITE_PRIVY_APP_ID=
